          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t4-23.4-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "factor proportional to magnitude stem:[F_\"D\"] of the drag force (<<t4-9.6>>)\nof a body moving in a fluid, dependent on the shape and speed stem:[v]\n(<<iso80000-3>>) of a body:\n\nstem:[F_\"D\" = 1/2 C_\"D\" rho v^2 A]\n\nwhere stem:[rho] is mass density (<<t4-2>>) of the fluid and stem:[A] is\ncross-section area (<<iso80000-3>>) of the body\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-1"
        }
      ],
